title: When does the Watch and Earn II quest come out?
body: I've already finished the first Watch and Earn quest and I haven't seen the second quest come out for me. Will it come out later or is it some bug?

replies.body: It's already out (I've already completed it myself). If it doesn't appear after a couple hours and a client restart, I'd recommend you submit a ticket to player support: https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new
